Package: fundfi
Type: Package
Title: Fundamental XBRL financial analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Wilson
Maintainer: Christopher Wilson <christopher@figaredo.net>
Description: This package acts as a wrapper for the edgarWebR
    and XBRL packages, making it easy to download any XBRL document
    from the SEC EDGAR's service. It also formats the balance sheet,
    income statement and cash flow. Finally it does percentage analysis,
    finantial indicators, variance and merging statements.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15)
Imports:
    edgarWebR,
    XBRL,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    pander,
    digest
Suggests:
    knitr,
    devtools,
    roxygen2,
    testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1.9000
